<tr ><td width="634" style="padding-left:33px; padding-right:33px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="BodyCopy" ><div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 35px;"><img src="http://pages.astrumsolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/SolarHeaderImage.jpg" border="0" alt="A special message from our Partner Program" width="634" height="171" /></div>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">Dear {{lead.First Name:default=Friend}},</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Thank you for being a valued partner. We appreciate your business and hope that we are continuing to support you as you grow your referral network. We have some exciting news for you!</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">We have completed an exciting brand transformation and our new name is Direct Energy Solar.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">While our website, collateral, and messaging have a new look and feel, our mission remains the same&mdash;to provide an exceptional customer experience and ensure that customers get the most out of their solar panels. <a style="color: #61af3f; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://partners.directenergysolar.com">Visit the Partner Portal</a> and start using our new collateral today!</p>
<p style="color: #1c3f94; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Take advantage of Direct Energy Solar&rsquo;s monthly promotion now through May 31.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Together we can increase our customer communications around going solar and generate even more excitement by taking advantage of limited-time promotions. Customers who meet with a Direct Energy Solar consultant for an in-home consultation <span class="appleLinksGray">by May 31, 2015</span> will receive a free* 6-month Heating &amp; Cooling Repair Essentials Plan from Direct Energy. This plan provides worry-free coverage for inconvenient repairs. Please note we are not offering this promotion in California or Pennsylvania.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;"><strong>The 6-month plan includes:</strong><br /> &bull; No service visit charge, no deductibles, no age restrictions<br /> &bull; $500 coverage per repair incident up to $2,000 annually<br /> &bull; 24/7 emergency service</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">In addition, customers receive $500 off their solar system when they sign <span class="appleLinksGray">by May 31, 2015.** This promotion is valid in all territories we serve.</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">If you have any questions regarding the promotion, please let me know. The weather is breaking (on the East Coast) so let&rsquo;s start talking solar. More conversations with your customer mean more money in your pocket.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Thank you for your continued support.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Suzanne<br /> <em>Sr. Manager, Field Marketing</em><br /> <span class="appleLinksGray">240-278-8616</span><br /> <a style="text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #61af3f;" href="mailto:suzanne.borneman@directenergysolar.com">suzanne.borneman@directenergysolar.com</a></p>
